'''''I Want to Be a Pilot''''' ni  filimi ngufi yasohotse 2006 yegukanye igihembo- ituruka muri [[Kenya]] - [[Megizike|Mexique]]  yanditswe inayoborwa na Diego Quemada-Diez. Iyi filime imaze kubona ibihembo mpuzamahanga birenga 50, harimo ''igihembo cy’abateze amatwi'' mu iserukiramuco rya Filimi rya Los Angeles kandi yitabiriye iserukiramuco rya firime risaga 200 nka Sundance, Locarno, Telluride, Edinburgh, Amiens, Los Angeles, São Paulo, Manhattan, Silverdocs, Bermuda, San Francisco .

== Umugambi ==
Filime ivuga amateka y'umuhungu wibasiwe n'ubukene muri kamwe mu turere dukennye cyane two muri Kenya ureba mu kirere kandi arota kuba umupiloti w’indege,.

